  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In triangle <math alttext=\"upper X upper Y upper Z\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>X</mi>\n\t<mi>Y</mi>\n\t<mi>Z</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>, the measure of angle <math alttext=\"upper X\"><mi>X</mi>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"90 degree\"><mn>90</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. Point <math alttext=\"upper W\"><mi>W</mi>\n</math> lies on segment <math alttext=\"upper Y upper Z\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>Y</mi>\n\t<mi>Z</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>, and segment <math alttext=\"upper W upper X\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>W</mi>\n\t<mi>X</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math> is perpendicular to segment <math alttext=\"upper Y upper Z\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>Y</mi>\n\t<mi>Z</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>. The length of segment <math alttext=\"upper W upper Y\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>W</mi>\n\t<mi>Y</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"572\"><mn>572</mn>\n</math>, and the length of segment <math alttext=\"upper W upper X\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>W</mi>\n\t<mi>X</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"429\"><mn>429</mn>\n</math>. What is the value of <math alttext=\"tangent upper Z\"><mi>tan</mi><mi>Z</mi></math>?</p>",
